00:46.380 --> 00:48.005
Are you trying to buy your statues back?

00:48.090 --> 00:50.675
l want them back for the chapel.
Coop wants them back for his wedding.

00:50.759 --> 00:51.759
lt's a win-win.

00:51.844 --> 00:55.430
l took a couple of patches,
might have been four.

00:56.598 --> 00:57.932
l took six.

00:58.934 --> 01:01.102
