09:21.186 --> 09:23.103
Yeah, he's okay.

09:27.776 --> 09:29.735
God, Fi, what did you do?

09:30.153 --> 09:31.695
We made a fire.

09:32.322 --> 09:33.781
l got caught.

09:39.287 --> 09:41.121
Answer your fucking phone.

09:42.332 --> 09:43.457
Nope.

09:46.294 --> 09:48.087
Hey, Jackie. Too much?

09:49.089 --> 09:51.048
lt's either him or me. You gotta pick.

09:51.132 --> 09:52.508
